cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GT 

The paper discusses the use of neotonic strategies in Genetic Algorithms for colour image segmentation, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves optimization techniques (cs.GT) and clustering methods (cs.LG) which further support the above categories.
